commit.message:
Do not update SSA in lto-stremaer-in

	* cgraph.c: Include tree-into-ssa.h
	(cgraph_node::get_body): Call update_ssa.
	* cgraphunit.c (cgraph_node::expand): Likewise.
	* lto-streamer-in.c (input_function): Do not call update_ssa.

From-SVN: r278943
